main event: Multiple residents of Woomera, Australia, reported seeing a green saucer-shaped object in the sky on the night of 22nd-23rd November 1953.
interesting points: The object was described as having bluish exhaust and disappeared above the clouds several times., Witnesses reported seeing the object traveling North at high speed., One witness claimed to see two flares dropping vertically in the Northwest., Independent accounts from different witnesses reported similar characteristics for the object., All witnesses were considered reliable and in a sober frame of mind at the time of the sighting.
sighted object: green saucer-shaped object in the sky
witness description: Woomera residents, including individuals employed in local government and a panel beater.
